m font-medium text-slate-700 hover:text-solar\" href=\"/battery-storage\">Battery Storage</a><a class=\"text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 hover:text-solar\" href=\"/how-it-works\">How It Works</a><a class=\"text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 hover:text-solar\" href=\"/solar-insights\">Solar Insights</a><a class=\"text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 hover:text-solar\" href=\"/partner-with-us\">Partner With Us</a><a class=\"text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 hover:text-solar\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a><a class=\"btn-primary\" href=\"/quick-quote\">Get a Quick Quote</a></nav><button class=\"rounded-lg p-2 lg:hidden\" aria-label=\"Toggle menu\"><span class=\"block h-0.5 w-7 bg-navy\"></span><span class=\"my-1.5 block h-0.5 w-7 bg-navy\"></span><span class=\"block h-0.5 w-7 bg-navy\"></span></button></div></header><main><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-navy text-white\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_right,rgba(215,166,58,0.28),transparent_38%)]\"></div><div class=\"container-shell relative flex min-h-[680px] items-center py-20 md:py-24\"><div class=\"w-full max-w-6xl\"><p class=\"mb-4 font-semibold uppercase tracking-[.2em] text-solar\">Cape Town Solar Matching Platform</p><h1 class=\"max-w-6xl text-5xl font-bold leading-[1.08] md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl\">Smarter solar connections for Cape Town homes and businesses.</h1><p class=\"mt-6 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8 text-white/75 md:text-xl\">Tell us what you need and get connected with a vetted solar installation partner suited to your property, budget and energy goals.</p><div class=\"mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4\"><a class=\"btn-primary\" href=\"/quick-quote\">Get a Quick Quote</a><a href=\"https://wa.me/27000000000?text=Hi%20RICO%2C%20I%20would%20like%20help%20finding%20a%20solar%20solution%20in%20Cape%20Town.\" class=\"btn-secondary\">Chat on WhatsApp</a></div></div></div></section><section class=\"border-b bg-white\"><div class=\"container-shell grid gap-4 py-6 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-navy sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-5\"><span>Cape Town focused</span><span>Residential enquiries</span><span>Commercial enquiries</span><span>Vetted partner network</span><span>No-obligation enquiry</span></div></section><section class=\"section-pad bg-mist\"><div class=\"container-shell\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-solar\">Choose your solar need</p><h2 class=\"mt-3 text-4xl font-bold text-navy\">A clearer path from enquiry to suitable solar support.</h2></div><div class=\"mt-10 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4\"><a class=\"card transition hover:-translate-y-1\" href=\"/residential-solar\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-navy\">Residential Solar</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\">Lower household electricity costs and improve energy resilience.</p><span class=\"mt-6 inline-block font-semibold text-solar\">Explore →</span></a><a class=\"card transition hover:-translate-y-1\" href=\"/commercial-solar\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-navy\">Commercial Solar</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\">Support operational continuity and reduce long-term energy exposure.</p><span class=\"mt-6 inline-block font-semibold text-solar\">Explore →</span></a><a class=\"card transition hover:-translate-y-1\" href=\"/battery-storage\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-navy\">Battery Storage</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\">Explore backup power and energy-storage options for your property.</p><span class=\"mt-6 inline-block font-semibold text-solar\">Explore →</span></a><a class=\"card transition hover:-translate-y-1\" href=\"/maintenance-upgrades\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-navy\">Maintenance &amp; Upgrades</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\">Inspect, maintain, expand or modernise an existing solar system.</p><span class=\"mt-6 inline-block font-semibold text-solar\">Explore →</span></a></div></div></section><section class=\"section-pad\"><div class=\"container-shell grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2\"><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-solar\">How it works</p><h2 class=\"mt-3 text-4xl font-bold text-navy\">Three steps to a better-qualified solar conversation.</h2><div class=\"mt-8 grid gap-6\"><div class=\"flex gap-5\"><div class=\"flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-solar font-bold text-navy\">01</div><div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy\">Tell us what you need</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-slate-600\">Complete the quick online assessment.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-5\"><div class=\"flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-solar font-bold text-navy\">02</div><div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy\">RICO reviews your enquiry</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-slate-600\">We assess customer type, location and solar requirements.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-5\"><div class=\"flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-solar font-bold text-navy\">03</div><div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy\">Connect with a vetted partner</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-slate-600\">A suitable solar installation company receives the qualified opportunity.</p></div></div></div></div><div><form class=\"grid gap-4\"><div class=\"grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2\"><div><label class=\"label\">Customer type</label><select class=\"input\"><option selected=\"\">Homeowner</option><option>Business owner</option><option>Property manager</option><option>Body corporate or estate</option><option>Other</option></select></div><div><label class=\"label\">Service required</label><select class=\"input\"><option selected=\"\">Residential solar</option><option>Commercial solar</option><option>Battery backup</option><option>Solar and battery</option><option>Existing system upgrade</option><option>Maintenance</option><option>Not sure</option></select></div></div><div class=\"grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2\"><div><label class=\"label\">Cape Town area or suburb</label><input required=\"\" class=\"input\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label class=\"label\">Monthly electricity spend</label><select class=\"input\"><option value=\"\" selected=\"\">Select range</option><option>Below R1,500</option><option>R1,500–R3,000</option><option>R3,000–R6,000</option><option>R6,000+</option></select></div></div><div class=\"grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3\"><div><label class=\"label\">Full name</label><input required=\"\" class=\"input\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label class=\"label\">Mobile number</label><input required=\"\" class=\"input\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label class=\"label\">Email</label><input required=\"\" type=\"email\" class=\"input\" value=\"\"/></div></div><div class=\"grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2\"><div><label class=\"label\">Installation timeframe</label><select class=\"input\"><option value=\"\" selected=\"\">Select timeframe</option><option>Immediately</option><option>Within 1–3 months</option><option>Within 3–6 months</option><option>Researching options</option></select></div><div><label class=\"label\">Preferred contact method</label><select class=\"input\"><option selected=\"\">WhatsApp</option><option>Phone</option><option>Email</option></select></div></div><label class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-600\"><input required=\"\" type=\"checkbox\" class=\"mt-1\"/><span>I consent to RICO contacting me about this enquiry and processing my information for this purpose.</span></label><button class=\"btn-primary w-full disabled:opacity-60\">Submit My Solar Enquiry</button></form></div></div></section><section class=\"section-pad bg-navy text-white\"><div class=\"container-shell grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2\"><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-solar\">Partner network</p><h2 class=\"mt-3 text-4xl font-bold\">Grow your solar business with qualified Cape Town opportunities.</h2><p class=\"mt-5 max-w-xl text-white/70\">Apply to join a future-focused partner network built around customer qualification, local relevance and accountable service delivery.</p><a class=\"btn-primary mt-8\" href=\"/partner-with-us\">Apply to Become a Partner</a></div><div class=\"grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"rounded-3xl border border-white/15 p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-solar\">Relevant enquiries</h3></div><div class=\"rounded-3xl border border-white/15 p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-solar\">Flexible commercial models</h3></div><div class=\"rounded-3xl border border-white/15 p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-solar\">Cape Town launch focus</h3></div><div class=\"rounded-3xl border border-white/15 p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-solar\">Future marketing support</h3></div></div></div></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"bg-navy text-white\"><div class=\"container-shell grid gap-10 py-14 md:grid-cols-3\"><div><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold\">RICO Luxury Solar Energy</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm text-white/70\">Connecting Cape Town homes and businesses with vetted solar installation partners.</p></div><div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-solar\">Explore</h3><div class=\"mt-3 grid gap-2 text-sm text-white/75\"><a href=\"/residential-solar\">Residential Solar</a><a href=\"/commercial-solar\">Commercial Solar</a><a href=\"/partner-with-us\">Partner With Us</a><a href=\"/solar-insights\">Solar Insights</a></div></div><div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-solar\">Contact</h3><div class=\"mt-3 grid gap-2 text-sm text-white/75\"><a href=\"tel:+27000000000\">+27 00 000 0000</a><a href=\"mailto:hello@ricoluxurysolar.co.za\">hello@ricoluxurysolar.co.za</a><span>Cape Town and selected Western Cape areas</span></div></div></div><div class=\"border-t border-white/10 py-5 text-center text-xs text-white/50\">© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> RICO Luxury Solar Energy (Pty) Ltd.</div></footer><div class=\"fixed bottom-0 left-0 right-0 z-40 grid grid-cols-3 border-t bg-white p-2 shadow-2xl md:hidden\"><a class=\"rounded-xl bg-solar px-3 py-3 text-center text-xs font-bold text-navy\" href=\"/quick-quote\">Quick Quote</a><a href=\